---
title: Middle Eastern Beef & Veggie Pizza with Garlic Yoghurt & Rocket
description: Roll up to a guaranteed favourite dinner with these speedy beef pizzas, infused with mild Middle Eastern spices. With peppery
rocket and a creamy yoghurt sauce smattered on top, these are a game changer!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/middle-eastern-beef-veggie-pizza-2058f0b6.jpg
